  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >State of surveillance - The Environment</h2>Game the high-security-system to extract the strictly protected files. <br>The Nexus is guarded by many hurdles though!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2207560/extras/b1d7fbf7af2616f4a5dfecacc11eff0d.poster.avif?t=1721831699\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2207560/extras/b1d7fbf7af2616f4a5dfecacc11eff0d.webm?t=1721831699\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2207560/extras/b1d7fbf7af2616f4a5dfecacc11eff0d.mp4?t=1721831699\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Look out! -  Sentinel</h2>If you don't beware the monitoring, more hostile forces may be alerted. <br>Don't let the Sentinel destroy you!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2207560/extras/2533c645e1245b98c3f51dbd4350ca52.poster.avif?t=1721831699\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2207560/extras/2533c645e1245b98c3f51dbd4350ca52.webm?t=1721831699\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2207560/extras/2533c645e1245b98c3f51dbd4350ca52.mp4?t=1721831699\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Hitch a ride - Data Packages</h2>Stow away on data packages to evade the Watchers gaze.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2207560/extras/9ee0cab8ccc5e7849059740f18ef9b1a.poster.avif?t=1721831699\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"